overview:
Dornan Consultancy offers a range of customised IT business consulting services, and specialise in providing advice and planning strategies, that will arm you to derive additional business value from the IT business solutions provided.

Problem solving shouldn’t be a problem. Dornan Consultancy can help you find and implement sustainable solutions.

Working with staff, clients and other stakeholders, Dornan Consultancy can help you identify and resolve a range of problems.

Dornan Consultancy can also offer a range of services, by engaging the right contacts, resources or vendors for the job.

Dornan Consultancy will project manage the delivery or ongoing management of the service.

Dornan Consultancy offers a range of services from something as simple as a small fixed price website, to ongoing setup and management of your complete online and digital marketing solution.

Project management can be useful to your business when you are unsure or unskilled in a specific area, and simply want someone to be a middleman and manage the vendor or supplier’s requirements.

Dornan Consultancy will use trusted third party contacts to take on the responsibility for delivering solutions and delivering successful projects.
